{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01F8MYALiUZQhAxqZYm9binF","type":"tool_result","content":"# workload.yaml Format\n\nBased on the issue body, the `workload.yaml` file should follow this structure:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: openchoreo.dev/v1alpha1\nmetadata:\n  name: <component-k8s-name>\nspec:\n  autoBuild: true\n  autoDeploy: true\n  endpoints:\n    - name: http\n      port: <port-your-app-listens-on>\n      type: HTTP\n      basePath: /\n      visibility:\n        - external\n```\n\n**Key requirements:**\n- The `port` field must match the port your application listens on (9090 for this todo-api service)\n- `apiVersion` must be `openchoreo.dev/v1alpha1`\n- `autoBuild` and `autoDeploy` should be set to `true`\n- The `endpoints` section defines how the service is exposed, with `visibility: [external]` for externally-accessible services\n- Adjust `endpoint type`, `basePath`, and add dependencies as needed for your specific component"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7a4126d9-69ca-4249-8836-57a0cbf0a094","uuid":"36a50d02-5e21-457b-b3bb-4ca89538d25d","timestamp":"2026-04-23T11:00:01.720Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":378219,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# workload.yaml Format\n\nBased on the issue body, the `workload.yaml` file should follow this structure:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: openchoreo.dev/v1alpha1\nmetadata:\n  name: <component-k8s-name>\nspec:\n  autoBuild: true\n  autoDeploy: true\n  endpoints:\n    - name: http\n      port: <port-your-app-listens-on>\n      type: HTTP\n      basePath: /\n      visibility:\n        - external\n```\n\n**Key requirements:**\n- The `port` field must match the port your application listens on (9090 for this todo-api service)\n- `apiVersion` must be `openchoreo.dev/v1alpha1`\n- `autoBuild` and `autoDeploy` should be set to `true`\n- The `endpoints` section defines how the service is exposed, with `visibility: [external]` for externally-accessible services\n- Adjust `endpoint type`, `basePath`, and add dependencies as needed for your specific component","durationMs":2718,"url":"https://github.com/asdlc-repos/kaj-test-15201/issues/1"}}
