{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01VQw7jJjpA1jF1oaLmYkCU7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01VFNVzbUTt6qR1F93o5Ev5o","name":"mcp__asdlc__submit_implementation","input":{"taskId":"19ca7f41-ed9d-49f0-926c-5a8c136bef10","summary":"Implemented the todo-api Go backend service with the following:\n\n- **store.go**: In-memory store using `sync.RWMutex`-protected maps for categories and tasks. Full CRUD methods for both entities. Deleting a category nullifies `categoryId` on all associated tasks atomically under a write lock. UUIDs generated via `github.com/google/uuid`.\n\n- **handlers.go**: HTTP handler functions for all endpoints. CORS middleware sets `Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *` and handles OPTIONS preflight. Validates required fields (400 on missing title/name), validates categoryId references exist (400 if not), returns 404 for missing resources, 204 for deletes, 201 for creates. All responses use `Content-Type: application/json`.\n\n- **main.go**: Server setup using `http.NewServeMux` with Go 1.22 method+path pattern routing. Listens on `:9090`. All routes wrapped with CORS middleware.\n\n- **Dockerfile**: Multi-stage build — `golang:1.22-alpine` builder stage compiles a static binary; final `alpine:3.19` image with CA certificates and tzdata for timezone support. Exposes port 9090.\n\n- **workload.yaml**: OpenChoreo service configuration with Docker buildpack, REST endpoint on port 9090, public visibility.\n\n- **go.mod / go.sum**: Module `todo-api` using Go 1.22 with `github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0`.","port":9090,"filesCreated":["go.mod","go.sum","store.go","handlers.go","main.go","Dockerfile","workload.yaml"]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":417,"cache_read_input_tokens":41176,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":417,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_token